      h2 'SCD Clinics' are sustainable community development learning and mentoring events
      p The vision of Umatiportal starts with the desire to see communites thrive.   Research is at the core of every good deciion, so this platform is designed to facilitate better research practices.  We provide software to help participants' form goals and to keep them track. SCD Clinics for by small groups or individuals interested in working on specific community development issues.  Inlusivity, transparency, efficienty, relocalization, cultural awareness are among the many contributing factors to consider.   SCD Hub's current body of research centers around water related community problems at this time.
    .col-md-6
      h2 Appropriate Technology
      p Umati Portal's primary goal is to assist SCD Hub with the development of its knowledgebase and to assist more people in contrinuting useful information to that project, such that it may help in decision making in community projects.
    .col-md-6
      h2 Water systems
      p As we learn more about water, we begin to see it as a living resource.  Water issues are complex and challenging.  Watershed planning begs the question.. "Can we increase watershed capacity? ie. re-foresting, erosion reduction, urban plantings, reduction of heat island effects.  Yes we can.

